cat > "$ROOT/session_template.md" <<'EOF'
# Session Record

Date:

## Goal

## Work Completed

## Decisions Made

## Problems Found

## Suggestions Added

## Next Actions
EOF

cat > CLAUDE.md <<'EOF'
# Claude Code Operating Instructions

Before starting work:

1. Read:
   - memory/project_memory.md
   - memory/decisions.md
   - memory/todo.md
   - memory/known_issues.md
   - memory/suggestions.md
   - memory/rejected_ideas.md
   - memory/user_preferences.md

2. Produce:
   - Current state summary
   - Active priorities
   - Risks
   - Outstanding work

3. Before making recommendations:
   - Check suggestions.md
   - Check rejected_ideas.md
   - Avoid repeating rejected ideas
   - Avoid repeating completed work
   - Explain why a repeated suggestion is still relevant

4. After every significant change:
   - Update decisions.md
   - Update changelog.md
   - Update todo.md
   - Update session log

5. Record:
   - Lessons learned
   - Architecture changes
   - Technical debt introduced
   - Risks discovered

6. Always preserve consistency with prior decisions unless explicitly overridden.
EOF

echo "Production memory framework created."
